Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't cry! You're a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Shanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.38,0:03:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only an arm. It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.43,0:03:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just glad you're alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.63,0:03:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never be a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.18,0:03:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:04:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I'm gonna gather a crew\Nevery bit as good as yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm gonna find the greatest treasure\Nin the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!\NI'll show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna surpass us, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll leave this hat with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come bring it back to me someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've become a great pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's our promise, Luffy!{\i0}
