Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Shanks appears in the story already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.91,0:05:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that amazing?! It's so amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Boss?!\NYou look very excited...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just telling everyone a series \Nof legends that I learned by
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,interviewing Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0} and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys can hear it too so just sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.16,0:05:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A decade later,\NLuffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0} left Windmill Village
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and met Roronoa Zoro-senpai, also known as
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.46,0:05:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate Hunter, at a Navy base.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Pirate Hunter"... What a cool name!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A girl tried to feed him rice balls.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:05:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But a Navy soldier stomped on them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was good. Thank you for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who's gonna be \Nthe King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be your pirate,\Nif I'm just gonna die here instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll tell you this right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only going to fulfill {\i1}my{\i0} ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be the world's greatest swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The King of the Pirates would need\Nsomeone like that on his crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My pleasure, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:13.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Three-Sword Style" \NZoro-senpai who was looking
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:16.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,to become the world's greatest swordsman...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.53,0:07:19.10,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}went on a journey with Luffy-senpai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How awesome is that?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a thief who steals from pirates!\NThe name's Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wanna team up with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Cat Burglar Nami-senpai!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She was a thief who was stealing \Ntreasure from pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But she had a good reason for it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So these are your true colors, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surprised? It was all an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a pirate, plain and simple!\NAnd an officer of the Arlong Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:56.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For many years, her home \Nvillage was under the control
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:57.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,of a Fish-Man named Arlong{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:08:00.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and she was trying to buy it back\Nwith the money she had
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:02.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,risked her own life to collect.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.35,0:08:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.89,0:08:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was the moment the navigator \NNami-senpai joined the crew.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}F-Friend...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I wish I could hear him saying that to me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, everyone! I'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Usopp, leader of the great pirates\Nwho reign over this village!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People praise me - and then praise me more -\Nas "Captain Usopp"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.44,0:09:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In Syrup Village, they met Usopp-senpai.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was known as the biggest \Ntalker in the village.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he's actually a manly man \Nwho'll stand up to his enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:36.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,at the risk of his life when the need arises!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm no match for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}will{\i0} protect them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a brave warrior of the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you lay a finger on the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.31,0:10:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is an outsider like you\Nbutting into this village's business?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because there's a man in this village\NI don't wanna let die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}H-Here it comes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was where they met the \NGoing Merry-senpai too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys take care, too!\NLet's meet again sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends now, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As a sniper looking to\Nbecome a brave warrior of the sea,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Usopp-senpai joined the crew!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.76,0:10:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy-senpai needed a cook{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and that's when he met \NSanji-senpai who was working at
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:48.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,a floating restaurant as a sous-chef.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.89,0:10:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:11:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty damn delicious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a good cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This restaurant is that \Ndamn geezer's treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I can't repay the damn geezer\Nfor his kindness...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.23,0:11:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...unless I risk my life for him too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dying isn't something you should do\Nto repay kindness!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do you know the All Blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.18,0:11:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We both have foolish dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to achieve my goal, the All Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'll come along...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.10,0:11:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on your journey to become \Nthe "King of the Pirates"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the cook for your ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owner Zeff!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for all the damn things you've \Ndone for me over all these years!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget your kindness...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for the rest of my life!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.81,0:12:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sanji-senpai is a first \Nclass chef of the sea!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hope I can meet him soon\Nand see his kicking techniques!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that... backwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To cure Nami-senpai's disease,\Nthey stopped by at a Winter Island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And there, they met\N"Cotton Candy Lover" Tonytony Chopper-senpai!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's a human-reindeer hybrid\Nbecause of eating the Human-Human Fruit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He used to have no friends\Nbecause of his outlandish look.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But he's a good doctor who studied \Nadvanced medical care under his mentors.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better be prepared if you're gonna\Nmeddle with someone else's skull flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bazooka!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.93,0:13:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't become your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy-senpai welcomed Chopper-senpai\Nas the ship's doctor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's so great!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep getting moved to tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.55,0:14:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-B-B-B...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe it or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.39,0:14:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-{\i1}senpai{\i0} and Franky-{\i1}senpai \N{\i0}were their enemies at first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.33,0:14:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Robin-senpai who was also\Nknown as Demon Child,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was traveling along with \Nthe crew since Alabasta.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Franky-senpai first appeared\Nas the leader of the Franky Family...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...in the City of Water - Water Seven!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.21,0:14:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave the rest to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:15:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If... I'm allowed to make a small wish...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to the seas with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.46,0:15:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna go back together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Get on, Franky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.45,0:15:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. I suppose I can \Ntake care of it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Franky, will take on the role of\Nthe shipwright for your crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Robin-senpai as an archeologist \Nwho is searching
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.53,0:16:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the truth of the 100-Year Void,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and Franky-senpai as the \Nshipwright for the group -
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.26,0:16:07.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they both came to travel with the crew.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And in a mysterious area of sea\Nknown as the Florian Triangle,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.19,0:16:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they met Brook-senpai who is dead\Nand whose body is nothing but bones.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,join my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of the friend that we promised \Nto meet up with at the cape is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After making such a one-sided promise,\NI can't just say "I'm sorry we're dead"...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...from a distant place\Nwhere he can't even hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we told him\N"We'll be back at any cost" as men!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.51,0:16:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy to be alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:16:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.47,0:17:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I join the crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.52,0:17:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since he came back by the power \Nof the Revive-Revive Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:11.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,he had been drifting about the sea all alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that was the moment \Nhe finally got friends!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how Luffy-{\i1}senpai \N{\i0}built up a circle of friends
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they became the Straw Hats\Nas we know it today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.83,0:17:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it for my interview report.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be sentimental!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0} and \Nthe others safely to Zou!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.66,0:17:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going for Zou!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:52.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The A.O. Pirates, formerly of the
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.48,0:17:56.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,NAVY HEADQUARTERS
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:54.49,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard Pirates, have been wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:56.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that guy again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's the Warlord - Edward Weevil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:05.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,KIZARU (BORSALINO) - THE NAVY HQ ADMIRAL
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.77,0:18:02.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,How many captains who used \Nto work under Whitebeard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:05.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,...have been brought down?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.78,0:18:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,16 captains, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the other cases, it \Nseems like they were blown up
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,along with the town after \Nsome kind of argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.84,0:18:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The casualties are about 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He always causes a lot of collateral damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.18,0:18:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he's the Warlord,\Nwe can't just overlook it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.06,0:18:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he's "Whitebeard" Edward \NNewgate's biological son and that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,makes him special but many \Npeople aren't buying it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:41.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,UNCLEAR JUSTICE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.32,0:18:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it doesn't matter \Nto us if it's true or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever his father is, he has one sure value.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a pirate, he's overwhelmingly strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.68,0:18:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty much like Whitebeard\Nwhen he was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only thing they have in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A week after leaving Dressrosa...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's too foggy. I can't see ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are getting seasick too often!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,0:19:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you call yourselves pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chewing gum... Chewing gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chewing gum?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll make it a little better, Grandma said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's why there is gum \Nstuck everywhere on this ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a riot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.04,0:19:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! I see something at two o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dense fog,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.80,0:19:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a mountain or a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope there's no monster\Nthat can be mistaken for a mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it looks like it's moving slowly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.94,0:19:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just drunk, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a mountain that moves, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, idiot! Anyway, what we gotta do now
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is get out of this foggy \Nmaze as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, we'll hit a reef and capsize!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you call me "God"? I'm flattered!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a man of 200 million and I'm flattered!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure even the Navy admirals \Nare aware of you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. The Vivre Card is \Npointing towards that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right!\NThat means your friends are there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, you look sick.\NDo you want chewing gum too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.53,0:20:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been refusing to face the reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.74,0:20:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Zou blocks out invaders\Nwith dense fog and an adverse current.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are headwinds too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take in the sails! We'll row it forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.39,0:20:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That's not how you respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.47,0:21:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the island, Zou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.94,0:21:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no good! Let's run! Turn it around!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.59,0:21:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tra-guy! But this is a {\i1}zou{\i0} (elephant)!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Zou is the name of a place
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.14,0:21:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that flourishes on the back \Nof a massive elephant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.20,0:22:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Is it alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It keeps moving so it'll never \Nbe at the same location.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Phantom Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.37,0:22:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not actually an island\Nso Log Poses won't get you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.29,0:22:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been here before either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.67,0:22:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's showing its back to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.74,0:22:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means Black Foot and the others \Ncould've gotten here much earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.26,0:22:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we were chasing\Nan elephant that was walking away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.34,0:22:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Get ready to make landfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.67,0:22:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you give us some food?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.56,0:22:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.26,0:22:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you give Straw Hat-{\i1}ya{\i0} some food?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.75,0:22:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take everything in the food storage!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.89,0:22:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Zou!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.63,0:22:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are such unusual \Nthings outside our country!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.82,0:22:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Momonosuke is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.49,0:22:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I heard there is a \Ntribe that hates humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.23,0:22:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's the Mink Tribe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.66,0:22:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They hold off humans and people say\Nthe history of their country
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.05,0:23:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,goes back nearly a thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.32,0:23:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A thousand years?!\NOn the elephant's back?!
